OL,3,CFormer Bishop of Liverpool offers
OL,4,Csupport to Government with
OL,5,CHillsborough Law
OL,7,FThe former bishop of Liverpool has
OL,8,Foffered his support to the Government
OL,9,Fwith the introduction of a
OL,10,FHillsborough Law.
OL,12,FThe Right Reverend James Jones, who
OL,13,Fchaired the Hillsborough Independent
OL,14,FPanel, believes the law should be
OL,15,Fshaped by families' experiences.
OL,17,FHe revealed he had contacted the Prime
OL,18,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer after the
OL,19,FGovernment committed to the to the
OL,20,Flegislation.
