OL,3,CFormer Bishop of Liverpool offers
OL,4,Csupport to Government with
OL,5,CHillsborough Law
OL,7,FIt would incorporate a legal duty of
OL,8,Fcandour, in the King's Speech in July.
OL,10,FIt follows a pathology review into the
OL,11,FHillsborough disaster, which called
OL,12,Ffor better communication after
OL,13,Fbereaved families were made to wait
OL,14,Fmore than 23 years for face-to-face
OL,15,Fmeetings.
