OL,3,CFormer Bishop of Liverpool offers
OL,4,Csupport to Government with
OL,5,CHillsborough Law
OL,7,FThe Right Reverend James Jones said:
OL,8,F"We're aware of other public
OL,9,Finquiries, we're aware of millions of
OL,10,Fwords being written about various
OL,11,Fpublic tragedies and the families'
OL,12,Ffeeling is there's got to be more than
OL,13,Fwords, there's got to be action and
OL,14,Fit's got to lead to change ` a change
OL,15,Fin culture and a change in law.
OL,17,F"So, the Hillsborough families are
OL,18,Freassured that in the King's Speech
OL,19,Fthe new Government has promised to put
OL,20,Fon statute the Hillsborough Law.
OL,26,@pD@AOUyD@AOU
