OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F398A1726083452
OL,3,CFormer Bishop of Liverpool offers
OL,4,Csupport to Government with
OL,5,CHillsborough Law
OL,7,F"I've written to the Prime Minister
OL,8,Foffering my help, having been involved
OL,9,Fwith the families, and I look forward
OL,10,Fto the Government reaching out to
OL,11,Fthose of us, especially the families,
OL,12,Fwho have experienced these tragedies
OL,13,Fso that future legislation can be
OL,14,Fshaped by the families' own
OL,15,Fexperiences.
OL,17,F"It would be sad if a Hillsborough Law
OL,18,Fwas produced and the families and
OL,19,Fsurvivors looked at it and said 'well
OL,20,Fthat wouldn't have made any
OL,21,Fdifference'.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
