OL,3,CFormer Bishop of Liverpool offers
OL,4,Csupport to Government with
OL,5,CHillsborough Law
OL,7,F"Let's listen to the families of the
OL,8,FGrenfell Tower scandal, of the
OL,9,Finfected blood scandal, of the Covid
OL,10,Fpandemic, of the Post Office scandal.
OL,12,F"Let's listen to the people that have
OL,13,Fbeen badly treated, learn from their
OL,14,Fexperience and change what needs to be
OL,15,Fchanged."
OL,17,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,18,F"This report is a stark reminder of
OL,19,Fthe extent to which the families were
OL,20,Ffailed and this government is
OL,21,Fcommitted to helping right the wrongs.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@IO]zD@AOU
