OL,3,CFormer Bishop of Liverpool offers
OL,4,Csupport to Government with
OL,5,CHillsborough Law
OL,7,F"We are introducing the Hillsborough
OL,8,FLaw, which will place a duty of
OL,9,Fcandour on all public servants and
OL,10,Fauthorities, building a culture of
OL,11,Fhonesty and integrity, and ensuring
OL,12,Fthat the institutional defensiveness
OL,13,Fand coverups seen in the wake of
OL,14,Ftragedies like Hillsborough are never
OL,15,Frepeated."
